OL,3,CGas workers in court following
OL,4,Cexplosion which killed 10
OL,6,FThree Jersey gas workers have appeared
OL,7,Fat the island's Magistrate's Court
OL,8,Ffollowing an investigation into a
OL,9,Ffatal explosion at a St Helier block
OL,10,Fof flats.
OL,12,FTen residents died following the
OL,13,Fincident at Haut du Mont in St Helier
OL,14,Fon 10 December 2022.
OL,16,FNeil Armstrong, 56, Lee Ward, 57, and
OL,17,FJohn Wright, 59, who all worked for
OL,18,FIsland Energy at the time, are each
OL,19,Fcharged with 10 separate counts of
OL,20,Fgross negligence manslaughter.
