OL,3,CGas workers in court following
OL,4,Cexplosion which killed 10
OL,6,FAppearing in court on Friday 14 March,
OL,7,Fthe men spoke to confirm their names
OL,8,Fand addresses, while the victims'
OL,9,Ffamilies watched on from the public
OL,10,Fgallery.
OL,12,FThe case was described in court as
OL,13,F"unprecedented" and "the most
OL,14,Fcomplicated in Jersey's history".
OL,16,FAll three men were later remanded on
OL,17,Fbail to appear for a plea hearing at
OL,18,Fthe Royal Court on Wednesday 28 May.
