OL,3,CGas workers in court following
OL,4,Cexplosion which killed 10
OL,6,FSeparately, Island Energy CEO Graeme
OL,7,FMillar appeared in the Magistrate's
OL,8,FCourt on behalf of the company that is
OL,9,Ffacing two criminal charges under
OL,10,FJersey's Health and Safety at Work Law.
OL,12,FThose alleged offences are failing in
OL,13,Ftheir duties to ensure the health and
OL,14,Fsafety of employees, and failing in
OL,15,Ftheir duties to ensure the health and
OL,16,Fsafety of persons not in their
OL,17,Femployment.
OL,19,FThe company is also due to appear at
OL,20,Fthe Royal Court on Wednesday 28 May.
